snippet.title: Half Life: Mod Showcase - The Specialists
snippet.description:
Pretty cool Half life mod, obviously inspired by The Matrix movies and Max Payne.
I know I kinda suck at the game, I was trying to show off all the stuff you can do with the dodge button, the third person view is also pretty neat.
